<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Laporan Transmisi Broadcast — Berani Cerdas</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      background: #0b0f19;
    }
    .glow-effect {
      box-shadow: 0 0 50px -10px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15);
    }
    .text-gradient {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #67e8f9 0%, #6366f1 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center p-4 relative overflow-hidden selection:bg-indigo-500/30 selection:text-indigo-200">

  <div class="absolute top-[20%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-indigo-900/10 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-cyan-900/10 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="w-full max-w-2xl z-10">
    <div class="rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 backdrop-blur-xl p-8 md:p-10 glow-effect">
      
      <div class="mb-8 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-400 text-2xl mb-4 shadow-inner">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-square-poll-horizontal"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Hasil <span class="text-gradient">Transmisi Bot</span></h1>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 font-medium">Laporan ringkasan pengiriman data broadcast via jaringan Telegram.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 mb-6 text-center">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 p-5">
          <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Total Sasaran</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-3xl font-black text-white font-mono"><%= users.length %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 border border-emerald-500/20 p-5">
          <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-emerald-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Berhasil</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-3xl font-black text-emerald-400 font-mono"><%= success %></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 border border-red-500/20 p-5">
          <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-red-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Gagal</p>
          <p class="mt-1 text-3xl font-black text-red-400 font-mono"><%= failed %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 to-slate-900/60 border border-slate-800 p-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-indigo-400 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-2.5">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-nodes text-[11px]"></i> Ringkasan Log Audit
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
          Broadcast dijalankan menggunakan metode alokasi antrean paralel. Riwayat log parameter, jumlah kuota terkirim, dan metadata lampiran telah sukses diamankan ke dalam database tabel <code class="bg-slate-950 font-mono text-[10px] text-indigo-400 border border-slate-800 px-1 py-0.5 rounded">broadcast_logs</code> di Supabase Cloud.
        </p>
        
        <div class="mt-5 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800/80">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-xs font-semibold mb-2">
            <span class="text-slate-400">Rasio Keberhasilan Jaringan:</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-cyan-400 font-mono"><%= successRate %>%</span>
          </div>
          <div class="w-full bg-slate-950 rounded-full h-2 border border-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-indigo-500 h-full rounded-full transition-all duration-500" style="width: <%= successRate %>%"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 border-t border-slate-800/80 pt-6">
        <a href="/admin" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-indigo-600 px-5 py-4 text-xs font-bold text-white shadow-lg shadow-indigo-600/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:from-cyan-400 hover:to-indigo-500 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-house text-[10px]"></i> Kembali ke Dashboard Admin
        </a>
        <a href="/admin/logout" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 px-5 py-4 text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 transition hover:bg-slate-800 hover:text-slate-200">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-right-from-bracket text-[10px]"></i> Keluar Sesi Login
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>